<item>
            <title>[SPARK-35955] Fix decimal overflow issues for Average</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-35955</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fix decimal overflow issues for decimal average in ANSI mode. Linked to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-32018&quot; title=&quot;Fix UnsafeRow set overflowed decimal&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-32018&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-32018&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-28067&quot; title=&quot;Incorrect results in decimal aggregation with whole-stage code gen enabled&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-28067&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-28067&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, which address decimal sum.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Repro:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
spark.conf.set(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;spark.sql.ansi.enabled&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;)

val df = Seq(
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 1),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 1),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2),
 (BigDecimal(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;10000000000000000000&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), 2)).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;decNum&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;intNum&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
val df2 = df.withColumnRenamed(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;decNum&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;decNum2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).join(df, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;intNum&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).agg(mean(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;decNum&quot;&lt;/span&gt;))
df2.show(40,&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should throw an exception (as sum overflows), but instead returns:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
+-----------+
|avg(decNum)|
+-----------+
|&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;       |
+-----------+&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
